Distribution. Onga River system, northern Kyushu: Fukuoka Prefecture . (
Nakajima et al. 2008
)

Habitat and biology. This species inhabits sandy-mud bottoms of the middle and lower reach of rivers. Although the spawning ecology is unknown, it is suggested that this subspecies needs a well-vegetated zone as a spawning site (
Nakajima et al. 2011b
).
